(81, 1, 1, NULL, 'AIGNER FIRST CLASS EDT 100ML', 'aigner-first-class-edt-100ml', 'AIGNER FIRST CLASS EDT 100ML', 'Buy AIGNER FIRST CLASS EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'AIGNER FIRST CLASS EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD76', 2, 1, '4013670003253', 0, '360.00', '147.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The fragrance is designed for a modern man of timeless elegance and understated, natural charisma, inspired by airplane traveling in first class. Aigner First Class is a fresh, slightly sweet and sparkling green fragrance with undertones of woods and moss. The composition opens with fresh and fruity tones of grapefruit, bergamot and apple, which refer to refreshing drinks that are served on the plane. The heart notes include spicy pink pepper, sweet melon and refined jasmine. Sensual aromas of patchouli, vetiver, amber and oak moss create the perfume&rsquo;s base.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'AIGNER FIRST CLASS EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(82, 1, 1, NULL, 'AIGNER LADIES DAY EDT 100ML', 'aigner-ladies-day-edt-100ml', 'AIGNER LADIES DAY EDT 100ML', 'Buy AIGNER LADIES DAY EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'AIGNER LADIES DAYEDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD77', 2, 1, '4013670000139', 1, '295.00', '126.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Ladies Day Paris by Etienne Aigner is a Floral fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Ladies Day Paris was launched in 2017. Top notes are bergamot, lemon, citruses and sea notes; middle notes are lily-of-the-valley, magnolia, rose, peony, jasmine and orange blossom; base notes are orris root, patchouli, musk, sandalwood and amber.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'AIGNER LADIES DAYEDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(83, 1, 1, NULL, 'AIGNER MAN 2 EVOLUTION M 100ML', 'aigner-man-2-evolution-m-100ml', 'AIGNER MAN 2 EVOLUTION M 100ML', 'Buy AIGNER MAN 2 EVOLUTION M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'AIGNER MAN 2 EVOLUTION M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD78', 2, 1, '4013670506273', 0, '210.00', '128.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Aigner |man|2 by Etienne Aigner is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. Aigner |man|2 was launched in 2007. Aigner |man|2 was created by Pierre Wargnye and Rosendo Mateu. Top notes are sage and sicilian lemon; middle notes are cinnamon, tarragon and anise; base notes are amber, patchouli, vanilla, cashmere wood, cedar and tobacco.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'AIGNER MAN 2 EVOLUTION M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
