(184, 1, 1, NULL, 'BENTLEY INFINITE INTENSE EDP 100ML', 'bentley-infinite-intense-edp-100ml', 'BENTLEY INFINITE INTENSE EDP 100ML', 'Buy BENTLEY INFINITE INTENSE EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BENTLEY INFINITE INTENSE EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD179', 8, 1, '7640163970029', 0, '245.00', '134.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Infinite Intense provides a long-lasting and stronger composition with a higher percentage of aromas (15%). Tart black pepper leaves stronger impressions in the opening of the composition, combined with geranium, lavender and violet. The heart abounds in spicy flavors by combining nutmeg with warm resins of Siamese benzoin, elemi resins and ambergris which ensures a modern masculine scent. The base develops warmth and precious shades of woody chords, patchouli extract, Haiti vetiver and Moroccan cedar, enveloped by the sensual scent of musk. The fragrance can be obtained as 100 ml Eau de Parfum.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BENTLEY INFINITE INTENSE EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(185, 1, 1, NULL, 'BENTLEY INTENSE EDP M 100ML', 'bentley-intense-edp-m-100ml', 'BENTLEY INTENSE EDP M 100ML', 'Buy BENTLEY INTENSE EDP M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BENTLEY INTENSE EDP M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD180', 8, 1, '7640111497547', 0, '388.00', '134.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Bentley for Men Intense by Bentley is a Oriental Spicy fragrance for men. Bentley for Men Intense was launched in 2013. The nose behind this fragrance is Nathalie Lorson. Top notes are bergamot, black pepper and bay leaf; middle notes are clary sage, african geranium, cinnamon, rum and woody notes; base notes are leather, benzoin, incense, cedar and patchouli.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BENTLEY INTENSE EDP M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(186, 1, 1, NULL, 'BENTLEY MOMENTUM EDT M 100ML', 'bentley-momentum-edt-m-100ml', 'BENTLEY MOMENTUM EDT M 100ML', 'Buy BENTLEY MOMENTUM EDT M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BENTLEY MOMENTUM EDT M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD181', 8, 1, '7640171190327', 0, '295.00', '144.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Momentum by Bentley is a Oriental Fougere fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Momentum was launched in 2017. The nose behind this fragrance is Nathalie Lorson. Top notes are bergamot, sea notes, nutmeg and violet leaf; middle notes are jasmine, ambergris and cashmere wood; base notes are sandalwood, tonka bean, moss and musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BENTLEY MOMENTUM EDT M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(187, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOADICEA THE VICTORIOUS COMPLEX EDP 100ML', 'boadicea-the-victorious-complex-edp-100ml', 'BOADICEA THE VICTORIOUS COMPLEX EDP 100ML', 'Buy BOADICEA THE VICTORIOUS COMPLEX EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOADICEA THE VICTORIOUS COMPLEX EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD182', 118, 1, '5060215061130', 2, '1250.00', '723.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>A fragrance for the confident and uncompromised, Complex is a blend of resins, incense and sensuous musk. Earthy and sensuous, it is filed with herbal notes of basil and sage, which give away to raw leather and animalistic notes. It is unusual and different &ndash; violet, incense &ndash; all this contribute to this sexy perfume.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOADICEA THE VICTORIOUS COMPLEX EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '3'),
