(221, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOSS WOMEN 90ML WHITE', 'boss-women-90ml-white', 'BOSS WOMEN 90ML WHITE', 'Buy BOSS WOMEN 90ML WHITE from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOSS WOMEN 90ML WHITE\r\n', NULL, 'PD216', 49, 1, '737052057989', 1, '317.00', '162.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 90, 5, NULL, '<p>The creator&#39;s first perfume, Hugo Woman, had an enormous success. Now the brand presents Boss Woman, a floral and fruity perfume to go with a new women&#39;s fashion collection (of sophisticated sportswear), specially designed for today&#39;s active woman. The opening scent of this trendy perfume is a blend of fruity notes (tangerine and mango) and kumquat. At its heart, freesia, orris, passiflore, while the base is warm from the blend sandal and cedarwood. Boss Woman was launched in 2000. The nose behind this fragrance is Sophie Labbe.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOSS WOMEN 90ML WHITE', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(222, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOTTEGA VENETA 75ML', 'bottega-veneta-75ml', 'BOTTEGA VENETA 75ML', 'Buy BOTTEGA VENETA 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOTTEGA VENETA 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD217', 10, 1, '3607342250826', 1, '490.00', '362.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Fragrance Bottega Veneta Knot is inspired by fresh air of the Italian coast, scent of flowers and clean laundry whose scent comes through the open windows. The fragrance is signed by perfumer of the house of Givaudan - Daniela Andrier, and provides top notes with a bunch of citrus shades originating from clementine, mandarin, lime, neroli and orange blossom. The fresh and optimistic opening notes add up to floral heart notes, among which are peony, white rose and lavender, posing a contrast to the earthy base of musk and tonka</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOTTEGA VENETA 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(223, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME 90ML', 'bottega-veneta-pour-homme-90ml', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME 90ML', 'Buy BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME 90ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME 90ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD218', 10, 1, '3607346504352', 0, '490.00', '284.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 90, 5, NULL, '<p>Bottega Veneta Pour Homme Parfum is announced as a bolder and more impressive interpretation of the original. &quot;Once again we find ourselves in the Dolomites, where the main character of this story has spent hours hiking in the crisp, cool mountains. As he retreats, he stretches out onto aged leather cushions, and their rich scent fuses with the fresh essence of cedar leaves clinging to his skin from the outdoors. The weaving of these sensual aromas creates a sophisticated intensity, marking the evolution of the signature scent into a richer rendition with long-lasting diffusivity. &quot;</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME 90ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(224, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME EXTREME EDT 90ML', 'bottega-veneta-pour-homme-extreme-edt-90ml', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME EXTREME EDT 90ML', 'Buy BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME EXTREME EDT 90ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME EXTREME EDT 90ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD219', 10, 1, '3607342751538', 0, '495.00', '296.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 90, 5, NULL, '<p>The composition is signed by Daniela (Roche) Andrier and Antoine Maisondieu. The fragrance is woody, aromatic and leathery, long-lasting and sensual. It retains the character and composition of the original, with enhanced accords of labdanum and pimento, which reveal the richness and character of the fragrance. Its aromatic - woody core remains the same, highlighted by intense leather accords.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOTTEGA VENETA POUR HOMME EXTREME EDT 90ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(225, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOUCHERON EDP L 100ML', 'boucheron-edp-l-100ml', 'BOUCHERON EDP L 100ML', 'Buy BOUCHERON EDP L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOUCHERON EDP L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD220', 119, 1, '3386460036351', 1, '272.00', '171.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Boucheron for women is a symbol of splendour, tradition and elegance, a classic floral oriental fragrance. Boucheron&rsquo;s designers created this elegant perfume in 1988 and it was inspired by the art of Parisian goldsmiths from Place Vendome. The fragrance in perfume concentration has a shape of a ring, edt and edp also have a symbolic shape of a ring. The basic notes are sweet floral-fruity ones with a spicy note of basil and bitterness of pelargonium, which slowly receives intensity with ylang-ylang, tuberose, daffodil, orange blossom from Morocco and jasmine. The base, which is as thin, opulent and elegant as the whole composition, encompasses: civet, benzoin, woody notes, Tonka bean, Indian vanilla, oakmoss, ambergris and musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOUCHERON EDP L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
