(231, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE EDP L 100ML', 'boucheron-quatre-intense-edp-l-100ml', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE EDP L 100ML', 'Buy BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE EDP L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE EDP L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD226', 119, 1, '3386460075664', 1, '395.00', '210.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Boucheron Quatre Intense by Boucheron is a Floral Fruity fragrance for women. Boucheron Quatre Intense was launched in 2016. Top notes are bitter orange, mandarin orange, red currant and strawberry; middle notes are jasmine and heliotrope; base notes are woody notes and vanilla.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE EDP L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(232, 1, 1, NULL, 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE M EDT 100ML', 'boucheron-quatre-intense-m-edt-100ml', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE M EDT 100ML', 'Buy BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE M EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE M EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD227', 119, 1, '3386460075688', 0, '365.00', '194.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>House of Boucheron, in cooperation with Interparfums, announces its new fragrance Boucheron Quatre inspired by the famous collection of Quatre rings. The feminine edition was launched and announced firs, coming out the spring of 2015. It is followed by the masculine version Boucheron Quatre Pour Homme. Quatre Pour Homme is an elegant woody fragrance for men with style. Its composition begins with fresh lime and lemon as well as violet leaves. The heart mixes notes of Sambac jasmine and rose, while the base captures predominantly woody tones of cedar and cashmere together with a trace of musk. Available as 50 and 100 ml Eau de Toilette.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BOUCHERON QUATRE INTENSE M EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(233, 1, 1, NULL, 'BRITNEY REMIX NAUGHTY W EDP 100ML', 'britney-remix-naughty-w-edp-100ml', 'BRITNEY REMIX NAUGHTY W EDP 100ML', 'Buy BRITNEY REMIX NAUGHTY W EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BRITNEY REMIX NAUGHTY W EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD228', 11, 1, '719346607094', 1, '245.00', '101.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The Naughty Remix is made for moments when you feel a bit dangerous and daring, while The Nice Remix is in touch with your softer side. Both fragrances are made to emphasize certain notes of the original. &ldquo;Fantasy is truly an unforgettable scent. Remixing the original notes to create new fantasy scents gives my fans and me more ways of expressing our inner fantasies - whether they&rsquo;re naughty or nice.&rdquo; Britney Spears.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BRITNEY REMIX NAUGHTY W EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(234, 1, 1, NULL, 'BRITNEY SPEARS  HIDDEN FANTASY L 30ML', 'britney-spears-hidden-fantasy-l-30ml', 'BRITNEY SPEARS  HIDDEN FANTASY L 30ML', 'Buy BRITNEY SPEARS  HIDDEN FANTASY L 30ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BRITNEY SPEARS  HIDDEN FANTASY L 30ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD229', 11, 1, '719346552851', 1, '94.00', '76.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 30, 5, NULL, '<p>Hidden Fantasy by Britney Spears is a floral fruity gourmand fragrance for women. Hidden Fantasy is a new fragrance and it was introduced in 2008. The nose behind this fragrance is Rodrigo Flores-Roux. The fragrance features sweet orange, tangerine, grapefruit blossom, verbena, clove, Napolitano cake, Stargazer lily, Sambac jasmine, vanilla bean, Jacaranda wood, sandalwood and amber.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BRITNEY SPEARS  HIDDEN FANTASY L 30ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(235, 1, 1, NULL, 'BRITNEY SPEARS FANTASY EDITION ANNIVERSAIRE L 100ML', 'britney-spears-fantasy-edition-anniversaire-l-100ml', 'BRITNEY SPEARS FANTASY EDITION ANNIVERSAIRE L 100ML', 'Buy BRITNEY SPEARS FANTASY EDITION ANNIVERSAIRE L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BRITNEY SPEARS FANTASY EDITION ANNIVERSAIRE L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD230', 11, 1, '719346601887', 1, '295.00', '119.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Fantasy is made of lychee, kiwi and quince at the top; jasmine, orchid, white chocolate and cupcake accord in the heart; and musk, orris root and woody notes in the base. Fantasy Anniversary Edition is a limited edition that comes in a special packaging - black bottle adorned with golden crystals and box inscribed with the names of her biggest fans from around the world. The bottles come with one of three different messages: &quot;10 hugs and 10 kisses&quot;, &quot;To my sweet scented fans for the decade of love&quot; and &quot;You are my inspiration,&quot; XOXO Britney. There are also 100 bottles that Britney personally signed.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BRITNEY SPEARS FANTASY EDITION ANNIVERSAIRE L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
