(252, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY BRIT EDT M 100ML', 'burberry-brit-edt-m-100ml', 'BURBERRY BRIT EDT M 100ML', 'Buy BURBERRY BRIT EDT M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY BRIT EDT M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD247', 20, 1, '5045252668009', 0, '335.00', '155.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Nonchalant Burberry Brit for Men is a perfect illustration of modern English spirit inwrought with tradition. Young English actor Hugh Dancy sitting in front of a fabulous old-timer embodies to perfection the laid-back, elegant spirit and philosophy of this new scent for men; demureness and irony, a classic turned into casual fragrance. Citrusy freshness of mandarin and bergamot and cool, spicy notes of ginger and cardamom preceed a masculine heart of cedar and nutmeg with a touch of refined wild rose. The base is sensual due to precious egzotic woods, gray amber, Tonka bean and patchouli. It was created by Antoine Maisondieu in 2004.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY BRIT EDT M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
