(275, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY SPORT ICE L EDT 75ML', 'burberry-sport-ice-l-edt-75ml', 'BURBERRY SPORT ICE L EDT 75ML', 'Buy BURBERRY SPORT ICE L EDT 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY SPORT ICE L EDT 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD270', 20, 1, '3386460030687', 1, '297.00', '161.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Burberry Sport Ice by Burberry is a Floral fragrance for women. Burberry Sport Ice was launched in 2011. Top notes are ginger, mandarin orange and water notes; middle notes are petitgrain, honeysuckle and magnolia; base notes are virginia cedar, sand and musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY SPORT ICE L EDT 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(276, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDP L 75ML', 'burberry-the-beat-edp-l-75ml', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDP L 75ML', 'Buy BURBERRY THE BEAT EDP L 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDP L 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD271', 20, 1, '5045411331843', 1, '336.00', '170.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Burberry&rsquo;s The Beat for women was released in March 2008. The parfumeurs in charge of this creation are Dominique Ropion, Olivier Polge and Beatrice Piquet, who enriched this perfume with the notes of tea from Ceylon, iris, bluebell, bergamot, cardamom, pink pepper, mandarin, light musk, vetiver and cedar. This perfume has connection with music, because the perfemeurs created it on the concept of music from Kasabian&rsquo;s album: Dirty Pretty Things, Razorlight, the Arctic Monkeys and The Fratellis, illustrating the mood introduced by The Beat. Baron and Bailey designed the bottle for the Beat and it respresents an enlarged version of Burberry&rsquo;s checked pattern painted on a scarft, which was worn by Deyn in the commercial. The bottle has a silver-coloured cap, as well as an amulet made of suede and metal, which was an interesting novelty in Burberries decorative/fashion accessories.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDP L 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(277, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDT M 100ML', 'burberry-the-beat-edt-m-100ml', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDT M 100ML', 'Buy BURBERRY THE BEAT EDT M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDT M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD272', 20, 1, '5045410681857', 0, '325.00', '161.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The Beat for Men by Burberry is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. The Beat for Men was launched in 2008. The Beat for Men was created by Olivier Polge and Domitille Bertier. Top notes are black pepper, citron and violet; middle notes are geranium and thyme; base notes are vetiver and woody notes.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY THE BEAT EDT M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(278, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY TOUCH FOR MEN 100ML', 'burberry-touch-for-men-100ml', 'BURBERRY TOUCH FOR MEN 100ML', 'Buy BURBERRY TOUCH FOR MEN 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY TOUCH FOR MEN 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD273', 20, 1, '5045252648988', 0, '275.00', '156.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Touch for Men by Burberry is a Woody Floral Musk fragrance for men. Touch for Men was launched in 2000. The nose behind this fragrance is Jean-Pierre Bethouart. Top notes are artemisia, violet leaf and mandarin orange; middle notes are nutmeg, white pepper and cedar; base notes are tonka bean, vetiver and white musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY TOUCH FOR MEN 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(279, 1, 1, NULL, 'BURBERRY TOUCH L 100ML', 'burberry-touch-l-100ml', 'BURBERRY TOUCH L 100ML', 'Buy BURBERRY TOUCH L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'BURBERRY TOUCH L 100ML', NULL, 'PD274', 20, 1, '3386463710203', 1, '324.00', '201.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>This perfume marked a revolutionary turning-point in the house of Burberry. Roberto Menichetti became an artistic director in 1998. With his arrival some serious changes had been made; a more modern style was implanted without being unfaithful to Burberry&rsquo;s original philosophy. British top model Stella Tennant became the face of the whole new trend. The fragrance is soft and casual with a hint of freshness in the top notes which include blackcurrant, cassis, cranberry, and pink pepper corns giving way to delicious floral middle notes. Rose, lily of the valley and jasmine mix with the notes of peaches and raspberries. The trail is comfortable as an English blanket, scented with warm notes of vanilla, cedarwood and oakmoss. It was created by Michel Girard in 2000.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'BURBERRY TOUCH L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
