(299, 1, 1, NULL, 'CARRERA POUR HOMME 100ML', 'carrera-pour-homme-100ml', 'CARRERA POUR HOMME 100ML', 'Buy CARRERA POUR HOMME 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CARRERA POUR HOMME 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD294', 36, 1, '618131009450', 0, '58.00', '50.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Carrera (original) by Carrera is a Aromatic Fougere fragrance for men. Carrera (original) was launched in 1988. Top notes are bergamot, lavender, coriander and rosemary; middle notes are anise, ginger, cloves and jasmine; base notes are cedar, tonka bean, musk, leather, sandalwood and oakmoss.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CARRERA POUR HOMME 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(300, 1, 1, NULL, 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE EDP 100ML', 'cartier-baiser-vole-edp-100ml', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE EDP 100ML', 'Buy CARTIER BAISER VOLE EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE EDP 100ML', NULL, 'PD295', 37, 1, '3432240026750', 1, '445.00', '225.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>This year&rsquo;s edition Cartier Baiser Vole, builds upon the oriental, mighty and passionate kiss of the dragon (Le Baiser u Dragon), announcing a more sophisticated approach and composition. The emphasis is on the game of excitement and anticipation. Mathilde Laurent, who composed the notes, is responsible for tempting stolen kisses of Baiser Vole release. The story of pure passion is told by the ultra feminine essences of rare and elegant lily flower. The scent is announced as intensively floral, fresh and powdery.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(301, 1, 1, NULL, 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE ESSENCE DE PARFUM EDP L 80ML', 'cartier-baiser-vole-essence-de-parfum-edp-l-80ml', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE ESSENCE DE PARFUM EDP L 80ML', 'Buy CARTIER BAISER VOLE ESSENCE DE PARFUM EDP L 80ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE ESSENCE DE PARFUM EDP L 80ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD296', 37, 1, '3432240032881', 1, '550.00', '216.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 80, 5, NULL, '<p>Cartier Baiser Vole Essence de Parfum comes out in September 2013 as a new version of the original scent Baiser Vole from 2011. Like the entire line, it also captures the scent of lily flower. Mathilde Laurent made sure that this time it is a lily in full bloom. Lily in full bloom accord, including petals and leaves, is highlighted by Bourbon vanilla. &ldquo;In this Essence de Parfum, we smell a lily in full bloom. It is a very soft, intense, voluptuous scent, as if we could bring our nose to the heart of the calyx. The open bloom offers up its sensuous perfume of vanilla notes while remaining light and lively,&rdquo; said Mathilde Laurent.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CARTIER BAISER VOLE ESSENCE DE PARFUM EDP L 80ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
