(351, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHANEL ALLURE EDP 100ML', 'chanel-allure-edp-100ml', 'CHANEL ALLURE EDP 100ML', 'Buy CHANEL ALLURE EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHANEL ALLURE EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD346', 9, 1, '3145891125306', 1, '605.00', '452.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Chanel describes Allure as: &quot;Difficult to define, impossible to resist. Clean and sheer, warm and sexy, ALLURE is a floral, fresh Oriental fragrance that finds an expression unique to each woman. Because every woman has her own special allure.&quot; And on the composition : &quot;Sparkling notes of Mandarin combine with the softness of May Rose and the sensuality of Vanilla. The Eau de Parfum &mdash; closest in strength and character to the Parfum form &mdash; features an intoxicating Passion Fruit note with a Peony accord and a warmer Oriental facet.&quot;</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHANEL ALLURE EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(352, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME EDT 100ML', 'chanel-allure-homme-edt-100ml', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME EDT 100ML', 'Buy CHANEL ALLURE HOMME EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD347', 9, 1, '3145891214604', 0, '470.00', '404.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>His allure, or pace, is determined, but lightsome. The composition is created of four main fragrant lines: green freshness, warm sharpness of pepper, strength and elegance of wood, and warm sensuality of labdanum, and tonka. None of these main lines can be sensed separately, together they create a harmonious whole. The top notes are mandarin, lemon, peach and bergamot; middle notes &ndash; freesia, geranium, rose and jasmine, and in the base &ndash; benzoin, tonka, sandalwood and vanilla. The perfume was created by famous Jacques Polge and launched in 1999.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(353, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME SPORT COLOGNE 100ML', 'chanel-allure-homme-sport-cologne-100ml', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME SPORT COLOGNE 100ML', 'Buy CHANEL ALLURE HOMME SPORT COLOGNE 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME SPORT COLOGNE 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD348', 9, 1, '3145891233209', 0, '420.00', '347.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>&quot;Allure in motion. More than a fragrance, ALLURE HOMME SPORT Cologne is a boost of well-being for the active man &mdash; a fresh, invigorating composition like a breath of energy. A generous citrus freshness is subtly heightened by spicy Lovage and Elemi notes and set against a backdrop of Cedar and White Musk.&quot; - a note from the brand. The fragrance was relaunched in 2016 keeping nearly the same olfactory composition (begamot could get tuned down a little in the top notes) with new packaging and sizes.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHANEL ALLURE HOMME SPORT COLOGNE 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
