(398, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE EAU DE PARFUM 50ML', 'chloe-eau-de-parfum-50ml', 'CHLOE EAU DE PARFUM 50ML', 'Buy CHLOE EAU DE PARFUM 50ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE EAU DE PARFUM 50ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD393', 34, 1, '3607346232347', 1, '430.00', '215.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 50, 5, NULL, '<p>The new eponymous eau de parfum by Chloe is quite a departure from the once-popular tuberose composition of the same name. A light and fresh yet seductively strong and self-possessed scent, the new Chloe fragrance is in no way its predecessor&#39;s timid younger sister. Just like all Chloe&#39;s bold, arty and free-spirited designs, the fragrance is feminine in a rather non-traditional, not all-out-girly way. Its accords expertly play against each other and they seduce the audience by being both elegant and daring at the same time.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE EAU DE PARFUM 50ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(399, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE LOVE EDP 75ML', 'chloe-love-edp-75ml', 'CHLOE LOVE EDP 75ML', 'Buy CHLOE LOVE EDP 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE LOVE EDP 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD394', 34, 1, '3607340205699', 1, '465.00', '252.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>The floral woody musky perfume from the house of Chloe, Chloe Love, is presented on the market in 2010. Love is a feminine and sophisticated floral composition, described to be powdery and soft. Noses Louise Turner and Nathalie Gracia-Cetto are credited for blending notes of orange blossom, pink pepper, iris, lilac, wisteria, hyacinth, heliotrope, powdery musk, talc and rice. Raquel Zimmermann is the face of the campaign.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE LOVE EDP 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(400, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE LOVE STORY EDP 75ML', 'chloe-love-story-edp-75ml', 'CHLOE LOVE STORY EDP 75ML', 'Buy CHLOE LOVE STORY EDP 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE LOVE STORY EDP 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD395', 34, 1, '3607342635876', 1, '495.00', '268.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Chloe Love Story is a new fragrance from the fashion house of Chloe, which comes on the market in September of 2014. Love Story is inspired by Parisian romance and the love padlocks on the bridge of the Pont des Arts; the campaign itself and the bottle design make this reference. Perfumer Anne Flipo composed the new Chloe floral composition, which explores the note of orange blossom. The scent is clean and fresh, made from neroli, orange blossom and stephanotis (jasmine from Madagascar).</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE LOVE STORY EDP 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(401, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE NARCISSE (L) EDT 100ML', 'chloe-narcisse-l-edt-100ml', 'CHLOE NARCISSE (L) EDT 100ML', 'Buy CHLOE NARCISSE (L) EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE NARCISSE (L) EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD396', 34, 1, '688575005035', 1, '255.00', '143.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Chloe Narcisse is a floral perfume dominated by daffodil. The perfume is very feminine, sweet, but with a bitter note. It is very intense, so be careful about the amount you use. The top notes include peach, pineapple, sweet orange blossom and delicate violet. The heart is made of gardenia, carnation, jasmine and rose. Cedar, sandalwood, vanilla and musk are in the base. Chloe Narcisse was launched in 1992. The nose behind this fragrance is IFF.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE NARCISSE (L) EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(402, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML', 'chloe-see-by-chloe-edp-75ml', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML', 'Buy CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD397', 34, 1, '3607345947686', 1, '410.00', '263.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Chloe fashion house is presenting a completely new perfume as a part of its urban and trendy See By Chloe collection, which probably marks the beginning of a new line of fragrances. See By Chloe fragrance is out by the end of 2012. The new fragrance is chic, elegant and energetic floral - fruity. The creation is signed by perfumer Michel Almairac. The composition opens with fresh notes of bergamot, apple blossom and leads to floral heart of jasmine and ylang-ylang. Its base is soft vanilla - musky with additional sandalwood accords.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(403, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML 3PCS SET', 'chloe-see-by-chloe-edp-75ml-3pcs-set', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML 3PCS SET', 'Buy CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML 3PCS SET from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML 3PCS SET\r\n', NULL, 'PD398', 34, 1, '3607347313557', 1, '435.00', '242.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Chloe fashion house is presenting a completely new perfume as a part of its urban and trendy See By Chloe collection, which probably marks the beginning of a new line of fragrances. See By Chloe fragrance is out by the end of 2012. The new fragrance is chic, elegant and energetic floral - fruity. The creation is signed by perfumer Michel Almairac. The composition opens with fresh notes of bergamot, apple blossom and leads to floral heart of jasmine and ylang-ylang. Its base is soft vanilla - musky with additional sandalwood accords.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHLOE SEE BY CHLOE EDP 75ML 3PCS SET', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(404, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD 1000 MIGLIA EXTREME EDT 80ML', 'chopard-1000-miglia-extreme-edt-80ml', 'CHOPARD 1000 MIGLIA EXTREME EDT 80ML', 'Buy CHOPARD 1000 MIGLIA EXTREME EDT 80ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD 1000 MIGLIA EXTREME EDT 80ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD399', 38, 1, '3607347802037', 0, '390.00', '244.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 80, 5, NULL, '<p>A man who takes part in the race, which serves as an imaginary model for this fragrance, must achieve three things: concentration, inner peace and unshakable self confidence.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD 1000 MIGLIA EXTREME EDT 80ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(405, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD AMBER MALAKI EDP 80ML', 'chopard-amber-malaki-edp-80ml', 'CHOPARD AMBER MALAKI EDP 80ML', 'Buy CHOPARD AMBER MALAKI EDP 80ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD AMBER MALAKI EDP 80ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD400', 38, 1, '3614220837345', 2, '475.00', '263.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 80, 5, NULL, '<p>Amber Malaki by Chopard is a Oriental fragrance for women and men. Amber Malaki was launched in 2015. The fragrance features amber, papyrus, incense, orange blossom, bourbon vanilla and labdanum.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD AMBER MALAKI EDP 80ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '3'),
(406, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD CASMIR L 100ML', 'chopard-casmir-l-100ml', 'CHOPARD CASMIR L 100ML', 'Buy CHOPARD CASMIR L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD CASMIR L 100ML', NULL, 'PD401', 38, 1, '3414208000040', 1, '395.00', '148.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Casmir by Chopard is a oriental vanilla fragrance for women. Casmir was launched in 1992. The nose behind this fragrance is Michel Almairac. Top notes are peach, apricot, black currant and raspberry; middle notes are mandarin orange, carnation and cinnamon; base notes are vanilla, benzoin, tonka bean and opoponax.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD CASMIR L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(407, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT BOUQUET DAMOUR L 75ML', 'chopard-happy-spirit-bouquet-damour-l-75ml', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT BOUQUET DAMOUR L 75ML', 'Buy CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT BOUQUET DAMOUR L 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT BOUQUET DAMOUR L 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD402', 38, 1, '3607341184870', 1, '260.00', '139.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Happy Spirit Bouquet d&rsquo;Amour by Chopard is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. Happy Spirit Bouquet d&rsquo;Amour was launched in 2013. The fragrance features yuzu, peony, rose, raspberry, cashmeran, musk, vanilla, nougat and sugar.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT BOUQUET DAMOUR L 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(408, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT L 75ML', 'chopard-happy-spirit-l-75ml', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT L 75ML', 'Buy CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT L 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT L 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD403', 38, 1, '3607347392163', 1, '330.00', '181.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Happy Spirit comes in a beautiful pink heart-shaped bottle that will for sure be liked by romantic girls. The fragrance is delicate just like the bottle it is captured in. The fresh citrus notes precede the balmy floral harmony of magnolia and honeysuckle, and sweet fruity raspberry nuance. The base is composed of cashmere wood, amber and musk. The fragrance comes as Eau de Parfum concentration in 30ml, 50ml and 75ml bottles and with matching body care products.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD HAPPY SPIRIT L 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(409, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD OUD MALAKI EDP 80ML', 'chopard-oud-malaki-edp-80ml', 'CHOPARD OUD MALAKI EDP 80ML', 'Buy CHOPARD OUD MALAKI EDP 80ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD OUD MALAKI EDP 80ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD404', 38, 1, '3607347336914', 3, '440.00', '278.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 80, 5, NULL, '<p>Composition of the new fragrance CHOPARD OUD MALAKI offers luminous accords of grapefruit in the very top of the composition, along with aromatic blend of artemisia and lavender. The heart accentuates masculinity with leather accords combined with tobacco and spices, while base notes highlight oriental notes with a combination of oud, ambergris and mysterious, dark, woody notes. Fragrance Chopard Oud Malaki can be obtained as 50 and 80 ml Eau de Parfum, available since 2012.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD OUD MALAKI EDP 80ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1'),
(410, 1, 1, NULL, 'CHOPARD WISH L 75ML', 'chopard-wish-l-75ml', 'CHOPARD WISH L 75ML', 'Buy CHOPARD WISH L 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CHOPARD WISH L 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD405', 38, 1, '3414208004284', 1, '148.00', '126.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Wish by Chopard is an Oriental Vanilla fragrance for women. Wish was launched in 1999. The nose behind this fragrance is Nathalie Lorson. Top notes are honeysuckle, black locust, orange blossom, coconut, gooseberry, Brazilian rosewood, pear, black currant and yuzu; middle notes are honey, violet, orchid, milk, heliotrope, lily-of-the-valley, jasmine, magnolia and osmanthus; base notes are sandalwood, amber, patchouli, vanilla, caramel, incense, tonka bean and toffee.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CHOPARD WISH L 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(411, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK BE M 100ML', 'ck-be-m-100ml', 'CK BE M 100ML', 'Buy CK BE M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK BE M 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD406', 24, 1, '88300104406', 0, '195.00', '104.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The theme of this collection is equality and emancipation. The message is We are one and design is adapted to the theme with the message which is inscribed on the bottles in different languages of the world. Besides clean, simple lines and minimalist design, new, limited editions turn to technological innovations and gadgets which are provided to users of various technological options in one product they choose for themselves. CK One and CK Be collections We are one are packed in see-through outer packages which have a soundbox in their base and it is compatible with MP3 format. It suggests that music knows no language barrier and it transmits clear feelings, no matter which language you speak. Speaker is placed on the front side of outer package.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK BE M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(412, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK BE M 200ML', 'ck-be-m-200ml', 'CK BE M 200ML', 'Buy CK BE M 200ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK BE M 200ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD407', 24, 1, '', 0, '210.00', '120.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 200, 5, NULL, '<p>The theme of this collection is equality and emancipation. The message is We are one and design is adapted to the theme with the message which is inscribed on the bottles in different languages of the world. Besides clean, simple lines and minimalist design, new, limited editions turn to technological innovations and gadgets which are provided to users of various technological options in one product they choose for themselves. CK One and CK Be collections We are one are packed in see-through outer packages which have a soundbox in their base and it is compatible with MP3 format. It suggests that music knows no language barrier and it transmits clear feelings, no matter which language you speak. Speaker is placed on the front side of outer package.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK BE M 200ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(413, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK BEAUTY L 50ML', 'ck-beauty-l-50ml', 'CK BEAUTY L 50ML', 'Buy CK BEAUTY L 50ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK BEAUTY L 50ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD408', 24, 1, '3607342139459', 1, '295.00', '126.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 50, 5, NULL, '<p>Elegance, sophistication, timelessness and beauty are in the first plan. The perfume is ideal for mature women who choose models from Calvin Klein collection and enjoy style and spirit of Klein collections. Beauty is a fragrance representing woman in her 40es, her beauty, maturity and self-esteem.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK BEAUTY L 50ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(414, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK BEAUTY SHEER  L EDT 100ML', 'ck-beauty-sheer-l-edt-100ml', 'CK BEAUTY SHEER  L EDT 100ML', 'Buy CK BEAUTY SHEER  L EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK BEAUTY SHEER  L EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD409', 24, 1, '3607342306134', 1, '395.00', '120.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The composition is floral &ndash; fruity, opening with notes of bergamot, red berries and peach Bellini. The perfume&rsquo;s core includes flowers of peony, pink lily and jasmine. The base is velvety due to accords of sandalwood, musk and vanilla blossom.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK BEAUTY SHEER  L EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(415, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK DOWNTOWN EDP 90ML', 'ck-downtown-edp-90ml', 'CK DOWNTOWN EDP 90ML', 'Buy CK DOWNTOWN EDP 90ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK DOWNTOWN EDP 90ML', NULL, 'PD410', 24, 1, '3607349363918', 1, '280.00', '112.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 90, 5, NULL, '<p>Downtown aims at a younger population which prefers sweet fragrances. The perfume is constructed as floral-woody and it was created by perfumer Ann Gottlieb of Givaudan. The composition opens in a foamy and dashy way, with notes of Italian lemon, bergamot, Tunisian neroli, green pear and aquatic plum. The heart incorporates gentle gardenia petals combined with pink pepper and violet leaves on a base of cedar from Texas, incense, vetiver and velvety musk Downtown arrives in four sizes of flacons and will be available as EDP. Besides the perfume, the collection also includes body lotion, body bath, body mist&ndash;body fragrance.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK DOWNTOWN EDP 90ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(416, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK ENCOUNTER EDT 100 ML', 'ck-encounter-edt-100-ml', 'CK ENCOUNTER EDT 100 ML', 'Buy CK ENCOUNTER EDT 100 ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK ENCOUNTER EDT 100 ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD411', 24, 1, '3607348541690', 0, '258.00', '110.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The composition is developed by Firmenich perfumers Honorine Blanc and Pierre Negrin. It opens with aromas of mandarin, cardamom and rum. Pepper, Egyptian jasmine, patchouli and cognac from the perfume&rsquo;s core, settled on woody nuances of oud, Atlas cedar and musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK ENCOUNTER EDT 100 ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(417, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK ENCOUNTER FRESH EDT 100 ML', 'ck-encounter-fresh-edt-100-ml', 'CK ENCOUNTER FRESH EDT 100 ML', 'Buy CK ENCOUNTER FRESH EDT 100 ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK ENCOUNTER FRESH EDT 100 ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD412', 24, 1, '3607349660826', 0, '275.00', '108.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Encounter Fresh by Calvin Klein is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. Encounter Fresh was launched in 2013. Top notes are bergamot and mojito; middle notes are cardamom, rum and lavender; base notes are labdanum, patchouli and sandalwood.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK ENCOUNTER FRESH EDT 100 ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(418, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK ESCAPE L 100ML', 'ck-escape-l-100ml', 'CK ESCAPE L 100ML', 'Buy CK ESCAPE L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK ESCAPE L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD413', 24, 1, '88300608409', 1, '235.00', '109.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>A romantic, feminine fragrance with with a hint of marine scent. Escape opens with camomile, apple, lychee, mandarine, rose, plum and peach, balanced by coriander and sandalwood. It was created in 1991. Here you can read our article&rsquo; Calvin Klein in step with time&rsquo;.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK ESCAPE L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(419, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK ETERNITY AQUA M 100ML 3PCS SET', 'ck-eternity-aqua-m-100ml-3pcs-set', 'CK ETERNITY AQUA M 100ML 3PCS SET', 'Buy CK ETERNITY AQUA M 100ML 3PCS SET from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK ETERNITY AQUA M 100ML 3PCS SET', NULL, 'PD414', 24, 1, '3614220739281', 0, '315.00', '169.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The new fragrance was created with an intention to presents a new face of Eternity edition for men, highlighted with a modern, casual, aquatic-woody composition. Eternity Aqua for Men opens with accords of cold cucumbers, citruses, lotus and green leaves. A heart blooms with a union of Sichuan pepper, Mirabelle plum, lavender and cedar, while a base finishes with sandalwood, Guaiac wood, patchouli and musk. The fragrance will be available from April 2010, as 30, 50 and100ml EDT.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK ETERNITY AQUA M 100ML 3PCS SET', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(420, 1, 1, NULL, 'CK ETERNITY EDP INTENSE L 100ML', 'ck-eternity-edp-intense-l-100ml', 'CK ETERNITY EDP INTENSE L 100ML', 'Buy CK ETERNITY EDP INTENSE L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'CK ETERNITY EDP INTENSE L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD415', 24, 1, '3614223162925', 1, '295.00', '147.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Eternity Intense for women reportedly intensifies the opulent floral composition of the originals, with energetic aquatic and additional floral notes. Iris gives it elegance and power, laid on the warm base of vanilla.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'CK ETERNITY EDP INTENSE L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
