(474, 1, 1, NULL, 'D&G 3 LIMPERATRICE 100ML', 'd-g-3-limperatrice-100ml', 'D&G 3 LIMPERATRICE 100ML', 'Buy D&G 3 LIMPERATRICE 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'D&G 3 LIMPERATRICE 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD469', 128, 1, '737052263137', 1, '395.00', '205.00', NULL, 1, 100, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The fragrances are advertised by celebrities, who are shown naked in advertising campaign made by Mario Testino. Women models are Naomi Campbell, Eva Herzigova and Claudia Schiffer, and men are: Noah Mills, Fernando Fernanes and Tyson Ballou. The collection The D&amp;G Anthology was inspired by tarot cards and their marks. The fragrances of this collection were named: Le Bateleur 1 (Tyson Ballou), L&rsquo;Imperatrice 3 (Naomi Campbell), L&rsquo;Amoureaux 6 (Noah Mills), La Roue de la Fortune 10 (Eva Herzigova and Fernando Fernandes), La Lune 18 (Claudia Schiffer). All fragrances will be available in amount of 100ml (3.4 oz) edt. D&amp;G Anthology L`Imperatrice 3 is advertised by Naomi Campbell, and the perfume features aromas of watermelon, kiwi, pink cyclamen and musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'D&G 3 LIMPERATRICE 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(475, 1, 1, NULL, 'D&G 4 LEMPEREUR EDT 100ML', 'd-g-4-lempereur-edt-100ml', 'D&G 4 LEMPEREUR EDT 100ML', 'Buy D&G 4 LEMPEREUR EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'D&G 4 LEMPEREUR EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD470', 128, 1, '737052263113', 0, '260.00', '192.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The D &amp; G Anthology collection from Dolce &amp; Gabbana appeared in 2009. The collection consisted of six fragrances that were named after the six different tarot cards. Each fragrance featured a top model as its image. The collection expanded with two new fragrances in 2011: La Temperance 14 and Le Fou 21. L&#39;Empereur 4 joins in 2012. D &amp; G Anthology L&#39;Empereur 4 (emperor, king, ruler) is a masculine fragrance that opens with lemon, bergamot and iris. The heart features aquatic accords and cedar notes, placed at the base of sandalwood, musk and tobacco.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'D&G 4 LEMPEREUR EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
