(541, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF COOL WATER SEA ROSE EDT 100ML', 'davidoff-cool-water-sea-rose-edt-100ml', 'DAVIDOFF COOL WATER SEA ROSE EDT 100ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF COOL WATER SEA ROSE EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF COOL WATER SEA ROSE EDT 100ML', NULL, 'PD536', 25, 1, '3607347462583', 1, '255.00', '119.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Davidoff launches a new edition of the women&#39;s Cool Water perfume from 1996. After Cool Water Sensual Essence edition that was presented in 2012, Cool Water Sea Rose launches in 2013 as a new chapter in the saga of love between a woman and the sea. Perfumer Aurelien Guichard created this composite of notes that represents freshness, spontaneity and purity. Initial accords include delicate and juicy Japanese Nashi pear, which wraps itself around the heart made of sweet floral notes of pink peony and laid on the sensual base of musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF COOL WATER SEA ROSE EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(542, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF ECHO M 100ML', 'davidoff-echo-m-100ml', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO M 100ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF ECHO M 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO M 100ML', NULL, 'PD537', 25, 1, '3414200800792', 0, '295.00', '107.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Echo is Davidoff&rsquo;s sixth fragrance, launched in 2003 and oriented to middle aged men. The fragrance includes aquatic notes, metal notes of aldehyds and white suede. The base notes are: chili, nutmeg, black pepper, musk, cedar, sandalwood and white suede. The bottle is very beautiful, ergonomic, created in an urban style. Echo was created by Alain Astori, Pierre Wargnye and Beatrice Piquet.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO M 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(543, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF ECHO WOMAN DEO SPRAY 100ML', 'davidoff-echo-woman-deo-spray-100ml', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO WOMAN DEO SPRAY 100ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF ECHO WOMAN DEO SPRAY 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO WOMAN DEO SPRAY 100ML', NULL, 'PD538', 25, 1, '3414200810074', 1, '130.00', '81.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The fragrance for men has got its match &ndash; Echo for women. Light fragrance with alternating floral, fruity and woodsy notes. Perfect for every-day use. The main notes are musk, iris, peony, osmanthus, violet, amber, cinnamon, and wood. It was launched in 2004. &quot;Echo Woman is a sensual and feminine fragrance that we anticipate willbring exceptional results here on the Australian market. We had recordsuccess with Echo Man, and I believe Echo Woman will follow in it&#39;sfootsteps&quot; Mr Gavin Blackburn, Managing Director Coty Lancaster.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'jpg', 'DAVIDOFF ECHO WOMAN DEO SPRAY 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(544, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF HORIZON M EDT 125ML', 'davidoff-horizon-m-edt-125ml', 'DAVIDOFF HORIZON M EDT 125ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF HORIZON M EDT 125ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF HORIZON M EDT 125ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD539', 25, 1, '3614220080499', 0, '360.00', '129.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 125, 5, NULL, '<p>The composition is made of woody, spicy and aromatic aromas. It is signed by perfumers Olivier Pescheux and Jacques Huclier. The fresh start combines pungent grapefruit and sweet mandarin with aromatic rosemary and fresh ginger. Cedar wood and spicy nutmeg are in the heart of the perfume, along with patchouli, black sesame seeds and South American pepper. Depth and sensuality is provides by the base made of vetiver and cocoa absolute.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF HORIZON M EDT 125ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(545, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF HOT WATER 110 ML', 'davidoff-hot-water-110-ml', 'DAVIDOFF HOT WATER 110 ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF HOT WATER 110 ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF HOT WATER 110 ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD540', 25, 1, '3607344163773', 0, '160.00', '95.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 110, 5, NULL, '<p>Davidoff Hot Water arrives as a fiery oriental, masculine fragrance in September 2009 on the market. Top notes feature absynth and red basil, a heart introduces hot accords of pimento and patchouli, while a base encompasses styrax and benzoin. The flacons is very appealing, coloured in dark red.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF HOT WATER 110 ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(546, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF LEATHER BLEND EDP 100ML', 'davidoff-leather-blend-edp-100ml', 'DAVIDOFF LEATHER BLEND EDP 100ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF LEATHER BLEND EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF LEATHER BLEND EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD541', 25, 1, '3607347778332', 2, '598.00', '208.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Davidoff Leather Blend comes in a luxurious container. The heavy glass flacon sports a rich translucent orange-brown hue. An elegant groove runs along the side of the bottle, adding to the distinction of its figure. The name of the fragrance is branded on a polished metallic sheet and Zino Davidoff&rsquo;s logo, a stylish double D icon, appears on top of the solid cap. An embossed golden tag and monogram adorn the refined and very masculine matching brown carton that retains the sophistication of the enclosed flask.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF LEATHER BLEND EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '3'),
(547, 1, 1, NULL, 'DAVIDOFF SILVER SHADOW 100ML', 'davidoff-silver-shadow-100ml', 'DAVIDOFF SILVER SHADOW 100ML', 'Buy DAVIDOFF SILVER SHADOW 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DAVIDOFF SILVER SHADOW 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD542', 25, 1, '3414200812016', 0, '160.00', '87.00', NULL, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Silver Shadow is an oriental woody fragrance which was presented in 2005. Fresh orange and spicy coriander open the composition, they lead to the mysterious heart combined of hot saffron and patchouli leaves. Warm, pleasant base notes feature sensual amber, benzoin and oakmoss.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DAVIDOFF SILVER SHADOW 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
