(607, 1, 1, NULL, 'DIOR MIDNIGHT CHARM L 50ML', 'dior-midnight-charm-l-50ml', 'DIOR MIDNIGHT CHARM L 50ML', 'Buy DIOR MIDNIGHT CHARM L 50ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DIOR MIDNIGHT CHARM L 50ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD607', 17, 1, '3348900756779', 1, '424.00', '331.00', 22, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 1, 50, 5, NULL, '<p>This romantic fragrance was created specially for the winter holidays of the 2006 season. Together with the new Dior&rsquo;s holiday&rsquo;s cosmetic line, it was meant to add to the festive mood. The bottle repeats the shape of the famous Dolce Vita, but this time it is decorated with feminine grace. Fresh and delicate opening is created of Italian mandarin, and green and fruity notes. Egyptian jasmine and Moroccan rose in the heart are accompanied with soft and velvety peach note. French Christmas specialty, candied chestnut, unites with the warm amber and a soft note of female skin scent. This limited edition comes in a 50 ml bottle. It was created in 2006.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DIOR MIDNIGHT CHARM L 50ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(608, 1, 1, NULL, 'DIOR MISS DIOR ABSOLUTELY BLOOMING EDP 100ML', 'dior-miss-dior-absolutely-blooming-edp-100ml', 'DIOR MISS DIOR ABSOLUTELY BLOOMING EDP 100ML', 'Buy DIOR MISS DIOR ABSOLUTELY BLOOMING EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DIOR MISS DIOR ABSOLUTELY BLOOMING EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD608', 17, 1, '3348901300049', 1, '595.00', '425.00', 29, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming is a new olfactory variation of Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet, designed as a sexier, more passionate and more modern scent. The hot pink color of the liquid matches the delicious floral character. The composition is comprised of three layers: red berries, Centifolia May rose from Grasse and peony, as well as white musk.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DIOR MISS DIOR ABSOLUTELY BLOOMING EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(609, 1, 1, NULL, 'DIOR MISS DIOR BLOOMING BOUQUET EDT 100ML', 'dior-miss-dior-blooming-bouquet-edt-100ml', 'DIOR MISS DIOR BLOOMING BOUQUET EDT 100ML', 'Buy DIOR MISS DIOR BLOOMING BOUQUET EDT 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DIOR MISS DIOR BLOOMING BOUQUET EDT 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD609', 17, 1, '3348900871991', 1, '680.00', '404.00', 41, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Fragrance bottle Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet takes the same shape as its antecedents and is decorated with a silver ribbon. The perfume is available as 50 ml Eau de Toilette and 100ml Eau de Toilette. Nathalie Portman is cover face of Miss Dior collection and features this advertisement as well as other advertisements of all more recent Miss Dior fragrances. Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet was launched in 2014. The nose behind this fragrance is Francois Demachy.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DIOR MISS DIOR BLOOMING BOUQUET EDT 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(610, 1, 1, NULL, 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE HAIR MIST L 30ML', 'dior-miss-dior-cherie-hair-mist-l-30ml', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE  HAIR MIST L 30ML', 'Buy DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE HAIR MIST L 30ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE  HAIR MIST L 30ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD610', 17, 1, '3348901255820', 1, '365.00', '257.00', 30, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 30, 5, NULL, '<p>It is created by the perfumer Francois Demachy: &ldquo;Perfuming the hair is an age-old gesture that is still just as elegant today, with just as stirring an effect. Miss Dior Hair Mist is discreet and appealing at the same time. An &lsquo;art of seduction&rsquo; that is subtly diffused soon as the hair moves&rdquo;.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE  HAIR MIST L 30ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(611, 1, 1, NULL, 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE EDP L 100ML', 'dior-miss-dior-cherie-edp-l-100ml', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE EDP L 100ML', 'Buy DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE EDP L 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE EDP L 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD611', 17, 1, '3348901016285', 1, '577.00', '425.00', 26, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>Top notes of Miss Dior Cherie L&#39;Eau will refresh you with aromas of bitter orange, which are delicate, fruity, bitter-sweet and delicately spicy. A heart is ruled by gardenia, a vibrant, opulent, white flower, while a base incorporates white musk, leaving a cotton-powdery effect and a long lasting feeling of cleanliness and freshness on your skin in a very soft and gentle way.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'DIOR MISS DIOR CHERIE EDP L 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
