(678, 1, 1, NULL, 'ELIZABETH ARDEN 5TH AVENUE 3PCS SET 75ML', 'elizabeth-arden-5th-avenue-3pcs-set-75ml', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN 5TH AVENUE 3PCS SET 75ML', 'Buy ELIZABETH ARDEN 5TH AVENUE 3PCS SET 75ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN 5TH AVENUE 3PCS SET 75ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD678', 44, 1, '85805188856', 1, '265.00', '147.00', 45, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 75, 5, NULL, '<p>Elizabeth Arden is an American fragrance, skincare and cosmetics company started by Canadian entrepreneur Florence Nightingale Graham in 1910. Graham used Elizabeth Arden as her professional name as well as the name of her company. The company&#39;s initial focus was on skincare and cosmetics, and they opened the first Red Door spa in Manhattan, soon expanding to major cities around the world as their empire grew.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, '', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN 5TH AVENUE 3PCS SET 75ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
