(681, 1, 1, NULL, 'ELIZABETH ARDEN ARDEN UNTOLD ABSOLU EDP 100ML', 'elizabeth-arden-arden-untold-absolu-edp-100ml', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN ARDEN UNTOLD ABSOLU EDP 100ML', 'Buy ELIZABETH ARDEN ARDEN UNTOLD ABSOLU EDP 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN ARDEN UNTOLD ABSOLU EDP 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD681', 44, 1, '85805169336', 1, '335.00', '137.00', 59, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The latest version is enhanced and more concentrated than the previous two, composed of a blend of luxurious flowers combined with red plum and black currant resting on a magnetic base of amber. Fruity notes of red plum and black currant leave a juicier and sweeter impression, blending rich floral aromas, additionally warmed with amber. The new version, UNTOLD ABSOLU is warmer, fruitier and more floral than the previous two, and arrives in a flacon with the same form as previous editions, in somewhat darker, golden-yellow shade.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN ARDEN UNTOLD ABSOLU EDP 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
