(685, 1, 1, NULL, 'ELIZABETH ARDEN SPLENDOR 125ML', 'elizabeth-arden-splendor-125ml', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN SPLENDOR 125ML', 'Buy ELIZABETH ARDEN SPLENDOR 125ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN SPLENDOR 125ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD685', 44, 1, '85805120900', 1, '120.00', '107.00', 11, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 125, 5, NULL, '<p>Splendor by Elizabeth Arden is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women. Splendor was launched in 1998. The nose behind this fragrance is James Krivda. Top notes are pineapple, wisteria, freesia, peony, hiacynth, apple, sweet pea and bergamot; middle notes are magnolia, tea rose, lily, poppy, orchid, jasmine, lily-of-the-valley and rose; base notes are sandalwood, amber, dark woodsy notes, musk, cedar and brazilian rosewood.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN SPLENDOR 125ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(686, 1, 1, NULL, 'ELIZABETH ARDEN WHITE DIAMONDS 100ML', 'elizabeth-arden-white-diamonds-100ml', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN WHITE DIAMONDS 100ML', 'Buy ELIZABETH ARDEN WHITE DIAMONDS 100ML from Al Hajis Perfumes', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN WHITE DIAMONDS 100ML\r\n', NULL, 'PD686', 44, 1, '719346022705', 1, '225.00', '131.00', 42, 1, 10, 1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 100, 5, NULL, '<p>The success of Elizabeth Taylor&#39;s fragrance has motivated many other celebrities to launch their own perfumes. White Diamonds is a sheer floral fragrance, an example of top classics. The harmony of flowers and aldehydes in the top notes, together with the sharp base, give this fragrance an elegant vintage nuance. The top notes are aldehydes, bergamot, neroli, orange and lily. The heart unites the classical trio, violet, rose and jasmine, accompanied by ylang-ylang, Egyptian tuberose and narcissus. The base is composed of oak moss, patchouli, musk, sandalwood and amber. The perfume was created by Carlos Benaim in 1991, and was inducted into the Fragrance Foundation&#39;s Hall of Fame in 2009.</p>\r\n', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-03-21 08:52:27', 1, 'png', 'ELIZABETH ARDEN WHITE DIAMONDS 100ML', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
